caption.p: GDC, rate performance test and cycle test of α-Co(OH) 2 nanowires and α-Co(OH) 2/α-Ni(OH) 2 nanorods, respectively. ( a, b) Discharge curves in three-electrode system ( c) their rate performance in three-electrode system, ( d, e) the discharge curves in two-electrode system, ( f), rate performance in two-electrode system, ( g) rate performance of single electrode of two materials in two-electrode system, ( h) cycling stability and coulombic efficiency of α-Co(OH) 2 nanowires and α-Co(OH) 2/α-Ni(OH) 2 nanorods.
